This is a JRuby on Rails on Google App Engine project created for a demo at JFokus 2010.


It should be runnable by on any recent MRI (C-Ruby) installation by first

#  sudo gem install google-appengine

And then:

Start development server (./script/server equivalent)

# dev_appserver.rb .

Open local console (./script/console equivalent)

# appcfg.rb run -S irb -r config/environment

Publish to production (edit config.ru with your application id)

# appcfg.rb update .


Inital setup was done by following the instructions here.
http://gist.github.com/268192

